# React Component Skeleton

Use with `adp-fend-react-component`. Replace placeholders before use and keep AD Ports tenant, security, observability, and test evidence requirements visible in the implementation.

```
import type { ReactNode } from 'react';

type <ComponentName>Props = {
  children?: ReactNode;
  tenantId: string;
};

export function <ComponentName>({ children }: <ComponentName>Props) {
  return <section>{children}</section>;
}
```
